OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F322A1784296099
OL,3,CAmbleside without drinking water for
OL,4,Cover 12 hours
OL,6,FHomes and businesses in Ambleside and
OL,7,Fthe surrounding area were left without
OL,8,Fwater for more than 12 hours.
OL,10,FThe issue affected supplies in the
OL,11,FLA22 postcode from around 10pm on
OL,12,FWednesday 15 July, until approximately
OL,13,F11am today (Thursday 16 July).
OL,15,FUnited Utilities says it was due to an
OL,16,Fissue with a valve on one of its water
OL,17,Fmains.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/8
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,323,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F322A1784296099
OL,3,CAmbleside without drinking water for
OL,4,Cover 12 hours
OL,6,FHeidi Knopfell, who runs a
OL,7,Fhairdressers in the town told ITV
OL,8,FBorder it was particularly a problem
OL,9,Ffor washing dye out of hair: "We gave
OL,10,Fthem the option to have the colour on,
OL,11,Fbut they would have to go home
OL,12,Fwherever they came from and then wash
OL,13,Fit off themselves. We couldn't do
OL,14,Fthat."
OL,16,FIt also presented a problem for
OL,17,Fchildcare and schools and nurseries
OL,18,Fleft without water. Heidi continued:
OL,19,F"My daughter, who works here as well,
OL,20,Fhad to bring the two little ones in to
OL,21,Fwork because nursery had to shut."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/8
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,323,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F322A1784296099
OL,3,CAmbleside without drinking water for
OL,4,Cover 12 hours
OL,6,FOne resident told ITV Border they were
OL,7,Ffortunate enough to have an emergency
OL,8,Fsupply of bottled water and a garden
OL,9,Fwater butt that could be used for
OL,10,Fflushing toilets, which they were able
OL,11,Fto give to neighbours as well.
OL,13,FResidents also found bottled water was
OL,14,Fin short supply, with shops rationing
OL,15,Fhow many each person could buy.
OL,17,FUnited Utilities said it delivered
OL,18,Fbottled water to priority services
OL,19,Fcustomers.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/8
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,323,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F322A1784296099
OL,3,CAmbleside without drinking water for
OL,4,Cover 12 hours
OL,6,FHowever, some residents criticised how
OL,7,Fwell they were updated, saying there
OL,8,Fwas very little communication.
OL,10,FGrace Jackson, who lives in Ambleside,
OL,11,Ftold ITV Border she reported the issue
OL,12,Fon the water company's website and was
OL,13,Fon hold for 15 minutes to then be
OL,14,Fgiven no timescale on when water
OL,15,Fsupplies would return.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/8
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,323,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F322A1784296099
OL,3,CAmbleside without drinking water for
OL,4,Cover 12 hours
OL,6,FShe added: "At 7:50am I got a text
OL,7,Ffrom United Utilities just saying they
OL,8,Fwere aware of an issue and they were
OL,9,Fworking on it. So that was actually
OL,10,Fthe first contact I'd had from the
OL,11,Fcompany.
OL,13,F"When temperatures are so high right
OL,14,Fnow, it's the beginning of the summer
OL,15,Fholidays, town is busy, the sun is
OL,16,Fout. Everyone needs water."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/8
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,323,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F322A1784296099
OL,3,CAmbleside without drinking water for
OL,4,Cover 12 hours
OL,6,FUnited Utilities says their policy is
OL,7,Fnot to bulk text overnight, "based on
OL,8,Ffeedback from customers" but
OL,9,Finformation does go on their website
OL,10,Fovernight.
OL,12,FThey argue it is "generally impossible
OL,13,Fto give timescales" because "these
OL,14,Fincidents are fast moving and things
OL,15,Fcan change very quickly. It can also
OL,16,Fbe the case that some customers have
OL,17,Fno water, others have some with poor
OL,18,Fpressure and others are unaffected".
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/8
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,323,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F322A1784296099
OL,3,CAmbleside without drinking water for
OL,4,Cover 12 hours
OL,6,FThe company adds, "We appreciate this
OL,7,Fcan be frustrating, it would be
OL,8,Fequally frustrating to give customers
OL,9,Fincorrect information."
OL,11,FA United Utilities spokesperson said:
OL,12,F"We apologise to customers in
OL,13,FAmbleside who had their water supply
OL,14,Finterrupted earlier today. Our onsite
OL,15,Fteam have completed repairs and
OL,16,Fsupplies are now restored. We thank
OL,17,Fcustomers for their patience."
